  "text": "The present findings raise questions for future research. For instance, do older adults' technology preferences align with performance outcomes? Would education and training about the benefits of new technology items (i.e., support for activities, convenience, features) increase technology use? Past research does suggest that training and education may increase technology adoption [CITATION_1] .",
